# Project 1: Everything Tech – UX/UI Design System

## 📖 Introduction & Overview

**Purpose of the Design System**  
The purpose of this design system is to provide a UI framework system that will be used across digital platforms which are web and mobile.

## 🎨 Design Tokens

### Colour Palette

| Category | Colour 1 | Colour 2 |
|----------|----------|----------|
| **Primary** | `#556AEB` | `#020A33` |
| **Secondary** | `#FF9500` | `#332200` |
| **Neutral** | `#FFFFFF` | `#000000` |
| **State Colours** | Success: `#6E82FE` | Warning: `#6C757D`<br>Error: `#FF9500` |

### Typography

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Font Family** | Inter (primary), sans-serif fallback |
