## 🧩 Component Guidelines

### Buttons

| Variant | Sizes | Interaction States |
|---------|-------|---------------------|
| Default | Small | Colour change |
| Hover | Medium | Shadow elevation |
| Active | Large | Border shift |
| Disabled | – | Reduced opacity, no interaction |

### Forms & Inputs

**Elements:** Text fields, Dropdowns, Checkboxes, Radio buttons

**Validation States:** Success ✅ · Error ❌ · Warning ⚠️

### Reusable UI Components

| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| **Cards** | Displaying grouped information |
| **Modals** | Overlay popups for additional details |
| **Navigation Bars & Tabs** | Primary user navigation elements |
| **Alerts** | Feedback messages for users |

